3851316e65badd0235353669f82d8ac322c87f00581" style=3D"color:#d40000;text-de=
coration:none;font-weight:bold" class=3D"sdf">Curious George Stephanopoulos=
</a></u></i>, relations between the two entities have descended to a post-I=
raq War nadir. =E2=80=9CFor what it=E2=80=99s worth,=E2=80=9D Dylan wrote, =
=E2=80=9Cthe vast majority of briefing room denizens I surveyed this week t=
hink [press secretary <b>Karine] Jean-Pierre</b> has lost all credibility.=
=E2=80=9D In <i><u><a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6I=
mRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dRckNBbmt6aEQ3aWFRM2hyaTB3ND0iLCJocmVmIjoiaHR0cHM6=
